<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">الْخَفْقُ:</span> اضْطِرَابُ الشَّيْءِ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> رَايَاتُهُمْ تَخْفِقُ وَتَخْتَفِقُ، وَتُسَمَّى الْأَعْلَامُ خَوَافِقٌ،<span class="c5"> وَالْخَفَقَانُ:</span> اضْطِرَابُ الْقَلْبِ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> رَجُلٌ مَخْفُوقٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَمَّ حَدِيثُ حُذَيْفَةَ،<span class="c5"> وَيَتْلُوهُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدِيثُ جَابِرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ رَحِمَهُمَا اللَّهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>